TextEng: Who are you? What are you doing in here?
Text: 당신은 누구죠? 여기서 뭐 하는 건가요?

TextEng: Cause? What cause?
I have to go now.
Who you be? What you do here?
Cause? What you mean?
Me want go now.
War golems? Catapults?
Is there anything I can do to help?
Text: 제가 도울 수 있는 게 있나요?

TextEng: Sounds like you turned tail and ran, Trancar!
Where are the Luskan forces now?
Me want help you. What me do?
Text: 나 도와주고 싶어. 나 뭐 해?

TextEng: You bunch o' cowards! You run like babies!
Where be Luskan army now?
I don't have time for this. I need to find Aribeth and Maugrim!
Text: 그럴 시간 없어요. 아리베스와 모그림을 찾아야 한다고요!

TextEng: Me no got time for this. Me need find Aribeth and Maugrim!
Text: 나 시간 없어. 나 아리베스랑 모그림 찾아야 돼!

TextEng: What must be done, Trancar?
What you need me do, Trancar?
And the golems?
Where can I find these wizards?
Text: 그 마법사들은 어디서 찾을 수 있죠?

TextEng: Where wizard be?
I'll destroy the golems and the catapults for you, Trancar!
What's in this for me?
Me destroy golems and catapults for you!
What me get if me help you?
Tell me about you and your men again.
Where can I find the catapults?
How can I stop the war golems?
Text: 전쟁 골렘을 어떻게 막을 수 있죠?

TextEng: I'm looking for Aribeth and Maugrim.
How goes the war effort?
Why you all here in this place?
Where me find catapults?
How me stop war golems?
We winning war yet?
Me look for Aribeth and Maugrim.
And a worthy song it would be, Trancar.
You story make a good song, Trancar.
Text: 네 이야기 좋은 노래 될 것 같아, 트란카르.

TextEng: I need to ask you some questions, Trancar.
Me got ask you questions, Trancar.
The bards don't sing about nobodies, Trancar.
Text: 음유시인들은 무명인사에 대해선 노래 안 합니다, 트란카르.

TextEng: Bards not sing 'bout nobody like you.
Text: 음유시인 너 같은 사람 노래 안 해.

TextEng: Can you spare any of your troops to help me?
Text: 병사 몇 명 빼서 저를 도와줄 수 있나요?

TextEng: You got any extra troops for help me?
Where will I find these wizards?
Text: 그 마법사들은 어디서 찾을 수 있죠?

TextEng: Where me find golem mage?
Asgard?
